- Use `will-change` sparingly and only for animated elements
- Avoid animating `width`, `height`, `top`, `left` (use `transform` instead)
- Use `backdrop-filter` with caution (performance impact)

**Optimization:**
```css
.animated-element {
  will-change: transform, opacity;
  transform: translateZ(0); /* Force GPU acceleration */
}
```

