  5% { --gradient-glow-x: 100%; --gradient-glow-y: 100%; }
  20% { --gradient-glow-x: 0%; --gradient-glow-y: 100%; }
  25% { --gradient-glow-x: 0%; --gradient-glow-y: 50%; }
  30% { --gradient-glow-x: 0%; --gradient-glow-y: 0%; }
  45% { --gradient-glow-x: 100%; --gradient-glow-y: 0%; }
  50% { --gradient-glow-x: 100%; --gradient-glow-y: 50%; }
  100% { --gradient-glow-x: 100%; --gradient-glow-y: 50%; }
}
```

### Card Glow Effect

**Description:** Animated glow that appears on card hover
**Trigger:** Hover state
**CSS:**
```css
.card-anime .animate {
  position: absolute;
  left: 50%;
  top: 50%;
  z-index: 0;
  aspect-ratio: 1/1;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  border-radius: 100%;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #250055, #0019ff);
  opacity: 0;
  filter: blur(60px);
  will-change: transform, opacity;
  transition: opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
}

